  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to evaluate the relative merits, safety and effectiveness of Transoral
      Incisionless Fundoplication (TIF) in GERD patients currently treated with daily Proton Pump
      Inhibitors (PPIs).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
